n NAIL Revitaliser from Mane 'n' Tail is a combination of moisturisers which
you massage into the cuticles each day to combat splitting and irregular
ridges. I have irregular ridges, so does the Grand Canyon, but like the tourist
attraction itself, they don't make me any less beautiful. Mane 'n' Tail hired a
clairvoyant to promote their product (why should you never go to the movies
with a clairvoyant? because they've probably seen it), and she says the shape
of your nails are a clue to your personality.
n If your nails grow down you have a controlling personality, if they grow up
you suffer from hypertension.
n If you have thin fingers you are spiritual and flexible and
anti-materialistic. Chunky fingers betray a sensual, stubborn, indulgent nature.
n If you have long fingers you are patient, broad-minded and pay great
attention to detail - the longer your fingers are in relation to the size of
your hands the more patient and painstaking you are. If you have short fingers
you are instinctive and impulsive. You do not suffer fools and you're an
excellent organiser, but you have a tendency to flirt with other women's men.
Shame on you!
n If you have small hands you are hard-working, energetic, earthy and
intuitive. You pull your sleeves up in a crisis. If you have large hands you
are broad-minded, artistic and expansive.
